Skip mangling for dev builds

Use compileBuildWithoutManglingTask for non-minified (dev) builds of
vscode-reh and vscode-reh-web targets. Mangling is only needed for
production (-min) builds and is both memory-intensive and slow.

The import is added as a separate statement to avoid conflicts when
upstream adds new imports from gulpfile.compile.ts.

